### Joker Agent Sample Interactions
### Use with the VS Code REST Client extension

### =====================================================
### Local Development Endpoints
### =====================================================

@localBaseUrl = http://localhost:7071
@agentName = Joker
@localAgentRoute = {{localBaseUrl}}/api/agents/{{agentName}}
@localHealthRoute = {{localBaseUrl}}/api/health

### Health Check (Local)
GET {{localHealthRoute}}

###

### Ask for a joke (JSON payload) - Local
POST {{localAgentRoute}}/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Add a security element to it.",
  "thread_id": "thread-001"
}

###

### Ask for a joke (plain text payload) - Local
POST {{localAgentRoute}}/run

Give me a programming joke about race conditions.

###

### =====================================================
### Azure Deployed Endpoints
### Replace <your-function-app-name> with your actual Function App name
### =====================================================

@azureBaseUrl = https://<your-function-app-name>.azurewebsites.net
@azureAgentRoute = {{azureBaseUrl}}/api/agents/{{agentName}}
@azureHealthRoute = {{azureBaseUrl}}/api/health

### Health Check (Azure)
GET {{azureHealthRoute}}

###

### Ask for a joke (JSON payload) - Azure
POST {{azureAgentRoute}}/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Tell me a joke about Azure Functions.",
  "thread_id": "azure-thread-001"
}

###

### Ask for a joke (plain text payload) - Azure
POST {{azureAgentRoute}}/run

Give me a cloud computing joke about serverless.
